Package: simplepivot
Title: Simple Functionality for Pivot-Table Style Transformations of Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Laurence", "Droy", email = "laurence.t.droy@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The main component of this package is the 'simple_pivot' function.
             This function can be used in conjunction with other piped data manipulation functions
             (typically at the end). The user selects rows and columns, and supplies a summary function 
             (with some useful functions provided by the package). Then the function returns a pivot-table
             style data frame, with the selected rows, columns, and summary values. 
